label: DEVICE
detail: Contains user-specified device status information.

label: ECODE
detail: Contains the current error code string.

label: ESTACK
detail: Contains the number of context frames saved on the call stack from a user-defined point.

label: ETRAP
detail: Contains a string of ObjectScript commands to be executed when an error occurs.

label: HALT
detail: Contains a halt trap routine call.

label: HOROLOG
detail: Contains the local date and time for the current process.

label: IO
detail: Contains the ID of the current input/output device.

label: JOB
detail: Contains the ID of the current process.

label: KEY
detail: Contains the terminator character from the most recent READ.

label: NAMESPACE
detail: Contains the namespace for the current stack level.

label: PRINCIPAL
detail: Contains the ID of the principal I/O device.

label: QUIT
detail: Contains a flag indicating what kind of QUIT is required to exit the current context.

label: ROLES
detail: Contains the roles assigned to the current process.

label: STACK
detail: Contains the number of context frames saved on the call stack.

label: STORAGE
detail: Contains the number of bytes available for local variable storage.

label: SYSTEM
detail: Contains system information about system objects.

label: TEST
detail: Contains the truth value resulting from the last command using the timeout option.

label: THIS
detail: Contains the current class context.

label: THROWOBJ
detail: Contains the OREF from an unsuccessful THROW.

label: TLEVEL
detail: Contains the current nesting level for transaction processing.

label: USERNAME
detail: Contains the username for the current process.

label: X
detail: Contains the current horizontal position of the cursor.

label: Y
detail: Contains the current vertical position of the cursor.

label: ZA
detail: Contains the status of the last READ on the current device.

label: ZB
detail: Contains status information for the current I/O device.

label: ZCHILD
detail: Contains the ID of the last child process.

label: ZEOF
detail: Contains flag indicating whether end-of-file has been reached.

label: ZEOS
detail: Contains end-of-stream status when reading a compressed stream.

label: ZERROR
detail: Contains the name and location of the last error.

label: ZHOROLOG
detail: Contains the number of seconds elapsed since Caché startup.

label: ZIO
detail: Contains information about the current terminal I/O device.

label: ZJOB
detail: Contains job status information.

label: ZMODE
detail: Contains current I/O device OPEN parameters.

label: ZNAME
detail: Contains the current routine name.

label: ZNSPACE
detail: Contains the current namespace name.

label: ZORDER
detail: Contains the value of the next global node.

label: ZPARENT
detail: Contains the ID of the parent process of the current process.

label: ZPI
detail: Contains the value of pi.

label: ZPOS
detail: Contains the current file position during the reading of a sequential file.

label: ZREFERENCE
detail: Contains the current global reference.

label: ZSTORAGE
detail: Contains the maximum available memory for a process.

label: ZTIMESTAMP
detail: Contains the current date and time in Coordinated Universal Time format.

label: ZTIMEZONE
detail: Contains the time zone offset from the Greenwich meridian.

label: ZTRAP
detail: Contains the location of the current error trap handler.

label: ZVERSION
detail: Contains a string describing the current version of Caché.
